int num=4567; --. 456
int sum=0; 

given any 4 digit positive value find sum of the digit without loop 

sum+=num%10; --> 7
num=num/10; --> 456%10===> 6
sum+=num%10; --> 13
num=num/10; --> 45
sum=sum+num%10; 13+5=18
num=num/10= 4
sum=sum+num%10; 18+4=22
num=num/10; 0 
sum=sum+num%10; 22+0=22

